// ============================================================================
// JUNGIAN ARCHETYPAL SUBDOMAIN ARCHITECTURE - COMPLETE BIMBA IMPLEMENTATION
// Coordinate System: #4.4.3-x-y (37 Total Nodes)
// Causal Domain: #4 Psychology (Fourth Domain - Final Cause/Telos)
// Branch: #4.4.3 Jungian Psychological Framework
